Comment: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Danger"\N"Building Planned for Demolition"\N"Demolition begins on May 19, 1997 at 1:00 PM"\N"No Entry"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:03.41,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A racing second hand, a shooting comet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.41,0:00:05.44,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}a pop-up doll, and broken ceramic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:09.08,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Mystery-solving logic is helpful against people's dry hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:13.02,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today is an exciting first errand! Exhilaration turns into terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:14.75,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.93,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
