Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:11.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs28}"Anniversary Big Bargain Sale Event"\N"First Errand Competition"\N"Beika Shopping Street"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad it's sunny out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:19.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:24.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good luck!\N- You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:37.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Group #1 has just left Beika Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:43.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What place will the Detective Boys' own Wataru-{\i1}kun{\i0} get?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get good shots, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Don't get left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Why do I have to do this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids'll be kids. Go get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Act more enthusiastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shopping street has some of your biggest clients!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:29.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we accept this job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:32.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:37.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the public will love us!\NWe asked really hard for the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:41.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So we asked for the job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem with that, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:48.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Never heard of such a detective group...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:58.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru-{\i1}kun{\i0} has just passed the vegetable store! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he can't buy a daikon!\NWhat will come of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:10.09,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We, the Detective Boys, were put in charge of recording the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.62,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It would later be aired on local TV, and the children would get prizes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.96,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}depending on their rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.93,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The rules are simple. Go alone from Beika Park
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:22.43,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}to Beika Shopping Street, some 500 meters away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.90,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}buy the items on the shopping list, and return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:30.47,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}However, no parents or onlookers can talk to or help them—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.84,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}they can only watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.14,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But it's actually tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:39.24,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Some kids keep coming back to ask their mothers for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.58,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}some kids get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:47.22,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}some buy toys and candy for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:51.09,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and some spend all their time in arcades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are kids too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His group's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}; he lives in my neighborhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't started yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's playing by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:23.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s items are a toothbrush, fried tofu, and a {\i1}shūgibukuro{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a {\i1}shūgibukuro{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:30.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a bag for kings, bishops, and pawns?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:31.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's chess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(358,430)}shōgi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:38.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Geez! Maybe you should enter too!\NIt'd be a good match!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:41.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have gotten far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:01.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This area is near your house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:06.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that his house is also nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,—went home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:14.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that. Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} is a loner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:21.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So was I. I often played alone, just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}In my own home, or nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.79,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.97,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:35.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}. Does he often play alone around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:39.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The empty lot! He's always playing there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bicycle track!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:12.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's fresh, and suddenly gets deeper.\NIt must've gotten heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:15.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}In other words, Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} got on the back of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to, Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:37.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:38.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:58.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:06.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He waved and ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he playing a joke on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:17.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}An abandoned building? What was he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Playing by himself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:31.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's finally at the shopping street! Will he be able to do his errands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:33.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First is the toothbrush!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:39.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He has to buy the toothbrush here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's gonna get the fried tofu first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:13.52,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What the... Someone cut this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:16.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Conan?! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:17.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A stationery shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he buying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One {\i1}shūgibukuro{\i0}, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. That'll be 200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a {\i1}shūgibukuro{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pure luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:44.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only two left! What will he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:44.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:07.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I put the side brake on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:32.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That rope and this car! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we lose him again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:40.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you weren't filming, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:41.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because {\i1}you{\i0} weren't, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:42.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:46.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Is someone out to get Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hiroshi's Yaiba figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally started his errands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:16.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He treasures this figure.\NIt's weird for him to just leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't go of his own accord! He was taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:27.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:33.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! But someone tried to kill him in fake accidents!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:37.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But they failed twice, so then—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:46.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is just a theory!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure they'd believe us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's find Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:57.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can call the police! I hope I'm wrong, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:22.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not that way, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:25.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should go to the cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:29.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Wait! If he {\i1}is{\i0} being targeted, then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Maybe that'll tell us where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:38.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta. Mitsuhiko. Play back all your footage of Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:45.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they tape something suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Go back a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Play that part again and pause it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:15.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:24.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely. In Genta's camera, he looks like he's waving at us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...but in Mitsuhiko's camera—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:30.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A curb mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:33.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} was waving at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:39.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More precisely, at a reflection of something in this mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:51.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The window!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:57.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was waving to someone in that window!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:01.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He didn't stop here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:05.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He had some kind of reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:10.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what does that have to do\Nwith him being kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(200,200)\frz-19\fry28\pos(186,152)\bord0\shad\c&H00&\fax0.3\fscx100\fnTele-GroteskUlt}DANGER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(200,200)\frz-21\fry28\pos(220,222)\bord0\shad\c&H00&\fax0.3\fscx100\fs18\fnTele-GroteskUlt}BUILDING PLANNED FOR DEMOLITION
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(200,200)\frz-22\fry28\pos(226,272)\bord0\shad\c&H00&\fax0.3\fscx100\fs18\fnTele-GroteskUlt}DEMOLITION BEGINS MAY 19, 1997 AT 1 PM\NNO ENTRY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:31.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The demolition is today! We don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Alright! I'll go in alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful—the floor is fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem to be in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Keep Out"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:10.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means nobody's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go downstairs, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A basement?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he's down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:26.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark to see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dead guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} dead too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An anesthetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:52.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was kidnapped and brought here... by the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:54.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is a dead body doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And why Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:04.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer planned to make the murder look like a demolition accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:12.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first floor was fragile; if any debris fell during the demolition,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:17.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the basement would be wrecked.\NThat was the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:20.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:30.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from his actions, I doubt he witnessed the actual murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:35.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the killer didn't know how much he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So they ran ahead to the shopping street—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:44.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,—but failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:50.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer eventually decided to fake his death too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:52.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:56.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty smart for a couple of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to kill us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:23.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking them so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:27.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} isn't back yet either. What could they be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:31.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably loitering around somewhere. Kids'll be kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this done quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. It won't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:49.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because you wouldn't call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:18:00.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who wanted to come in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:10.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The demolition's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Running water? Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We might survive, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:55.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying! They'll come back! Kids'll be kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:59.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if something bad has happened to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pulling so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:24.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:36.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've been crushed along with that dead body,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:41.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to the weak support struts,\Nthe basement wall crumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:44.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, it led right into an underground tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:07.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! You have another store, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:14.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried tofu and one toothbrush, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:30.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:37.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That was your convenience store, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:43.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dirty stockbroker tricked me,\Nand I racked up more debt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:48.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,than I could ever pay off,\Nand my family ran out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that stockbroker that I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:57.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My store was repossessed and shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't as popular as stores on the shopping street—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be quickly forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} remembered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:11.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to buy from your store for his first errand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:15.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:18.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He did...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The very same Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} that you tried to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:25.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, little boy! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:34.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge victory for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:06.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's what happened? Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:11.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess kids'll be kids. How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:14.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll have a bath, some booze,\Nand get some shut-eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:16.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:20.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where's Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.57,0:23:22.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:23.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:29.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What were his last two things again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:31.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, fried tofu and—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:32.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A toothbrush!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:35.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go, Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:44.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What the heck am I doing? Why am I stuck doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:24:09.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(134,104)\fnSegoe\fscx105\fs28\fsp1\shad0\bord0\alpha&H1F&}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.33,0:23:47.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you looking at, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:50.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching that apartment's balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:56.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}She jumped off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:24:01.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This was a murder!\NMeaning the most suspicious person is—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}—the guy on the phone who told her not to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.95,0:24:08.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But how could he do it from so far away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:14.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(320,64)}Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:14.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,234)\a6\fscx100\fscy100\fnDINk\c&HFFFFFF&\b0\fs32\bord0\shad0}The Illustrator Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:20.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Contact Lens Set
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.00,0:24:25.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(314,396)\alpha&H1F&\fnSegoe\fscx100\bord0\shad0\fs22}Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time, a glimpse into the adult world!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.39,0:24:24.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wait, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, don't look!
